rows.label: qst100306_msg0002
rows.name:
The one who gave Pupun food,
defeated the Vacuum Grogg, and
gathered the repair materials!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to your help, I was able
to successfully complete 40
hours of flight training, mo!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0004
rows.name:
I got my license, too... I'm a
full-fledged Nopon pilot, mo!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0006
rows.name:
...A reward for the food?
...The cost of the materials?

rows.label: qst100306_msg0007
rows.name:
Ah, um... I haven't started working
yet... And the training fees...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0008
rows.name:
Ah! I feel like my skills
are getting rusty, mo!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0009
rows.name:
If I take a break between flights,
my skills will get rusty, mo!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0010
rows.name:
I have to go fly right now,
mo! Well then, goodbye, mo!
